window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I had no idea how beautiful and terrifying my life was about to become.</p> <p>Living as an independent artist in New York, I was soon faced with the new knowledge of my powers, a curse, and how bonding with five sexy-as-sin supernaturals would break that curse.</p> <p>One by one they found me—Fae, Warlock, Demon, Wolf shifter, Vampire. I'm their mate. Their equal. Their perfect match. The one to unbind them from their curse. Heart, body, and soul, I'm meant to be theirs. Theirs to share. Theirs to love.</p> <p>From the beginning, they warn me of my fate. The stronger our magic bonds; the greater the chance evil will find us. These incredible beings will give their lives to protect me, no matter the sacrifice, but I'm not willing to lose any of them. They've stolen my heart and I'll do whatever it takes to break the curse and stop the one who's coming for us.</p>"; 
